plot: The Corrs, the Irish sibling supergroup, play a special St. Patrick's Day concert at Britain's famous Royal Albert Hall to coincide with the release of their sophomore album, &"Talk On Corners.&" Special guest Mick Fleetwood plays drums for three songs, including &"Dreams,&" &"Haste to the Wedding,&" and &"Toss the Feathers.&"   Written by  Doug Rusley
title: The Corrs: 'Live at the Royal Albert Hall' - St. Patrick's Day March 17, 1998
